abstract.t:
This document specifies instance-related messages to be used in
conjunction with the Semantic Definition Format (SDF) for Data and
Interactions of Things (draft-ietf-asdf-sdf).  Split into four
"archetypes", instance-related messages are always governed by SDF
models, strictly separating instance and class information. _Context_
information plays a crucial role both for lifecycle management and
actual device interaction.


// This revision applies a major restructuring, reduces redundancy
// and clarifies some of the concepts that are used throughout the
// document.  It also expands upon three experimental application
// scenarios for instance-related messages.
